Content:
@LabsAssistant  
Please `./start.sh`
I have got spent utxo detection working, rather than banning after the fact, it stops bad utxos even being sent to recvmask. üôÇ 
Along with this I wrote a new utxo cache that leverages the wallet filter to remove any utxo that has been spent from the cache upon receive to mempool. Rather than needing to reset it entirly every time. This should fix the last of the issues ü§û
